			<text>DPIC
DPIC
Goes to location of dive emergency
Informs Duty Op &amp; directs Animal Care divers
Determines that an accident has occurred and will call EMS/911 or radio for additional staff as needed
Determines whether it is safe to approach the injured diver
Manages the diving emergency (assessment, first aid, extrication, buoyancy)
Notifies VP/COO and Director of Animal Care
Completes an incident report and submits to DSO</text>
