			<notes/>
			<notesNormalized/>
			<notesHtml/>
			<text>Conscious Injured Diver
Spinal Injury Suspected
Buddy or Tender enters the water to help calm the injured diver and keep them immobile
Establish positive buoyancy for the injured diver
Wait for EMS to arrive to extricate from exhibit
Continue to monitor injured diver for changes in consciousness
Life-threatening Injury
e.g. severe bleeding
Remove injured diver in most expedient manner
Keep injured diver as immobile as possible
Do not delay removing injured diver from water</text>
		</slide>
		<slide index="11" title="Unconscious Injured Diver" titleNormalized="unconscious injured diver" src="slide12.swf" size="1998" advanceOnTime="0" framesCount="1" hasEmbeddedFlashClip="0" hidden="0" level="0" advanceOnClick="1" thumbnailAssetId="">
